            "text": "BILL's AI doesn't just OCR your invoices—it *understands* them. Upload a PDF or forward an email, and the system extracts vendor name, line items, amounts, due dates, and GL codes with remarkable accuracy. It learns your patterns over time, so the more you use it, the fewer corrections you need to make.",
